"口：“好吧……虽然他们是外人，但看来……跟那些狂热信徒倒是挺合得来。”随后便是一片"
"寂静。当你独自凝视着黑暗时，很快就意识到，自己有多庆幸刚才这场荒唐的消遣。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:623
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者信徒）没错。我自己都有教派了，一应俱全。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:625
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/text"
msgstr "“你自己的……教派？”其中一个问道，稍微想了想又继续说，“那……我能加入吗？”"

