msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "那必须的！这儿可是派对现场！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:629
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那名深渊潜者尖叫着冲出房间，冲向传送器。片刻之后，他直接被传送到了你的房间里"
"，并且继续尖叫。通过通讯频道，其他深渊潜者也在尖叫。你的启蒙派信徒也在尖叫。"
"他们似乎完全不会累，就这么一直尖叫下去。最终，如同所有美好的事物一般，这一切"
"总得结束……而结局就是你低声嘟囔了几句，挂断通讯，并下令启动超光速引擎。那个声"
"音只是觉得好笑，轻笑了起来。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:635
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "没门。酷劲儿可是有限度的……毕竟供需关系摆在那儿呢。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:637
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"起初，它似乎对你的回答感到难过，但随即带着一股坚定的神情离开了房间。片刻之后"
"，它抱着尽可能多的废料回来了！“如果……我不能直接加入你的教派……我就在这里以你……"
"伟大的名义建立第二个教派！求你……求求你，收下这份祭品吧！”大多数神祇可能会因为"
"被献上一堆垃圾而感到被冒犯，但你呢？很难再找到比这更好的礼物了……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:640
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:642
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"废料被传送过来，在你挂断与新信徒们的通讯后，那个声音开口道：“这东西的价值……比"
"你想象的要大。伪神的力量……源于信仰。信仰对你我而言毫无用处，但对它而言……却是"
"一切。至少可以说，策反它的追随者这件事很有趣，但同时……这也是一种战术优势。”随"
"后它陷入沉默，留下你独自思考信仰之力的运作原理……你推测，这对神明来说，大概就"
"像废料对你一样重要。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:651
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "开什么玩笑？我恨死那个黑暗之神了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:653
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"所有深渊潜者立刻齐声静止，一动不动。通讯突然中断时，他们全都直直地盯着你。你"
"完全想不通他们是怎么做到不动却还能做到这一点的……还没等你细想，就发现他们的飞"
"船已经转向你这边，武器正在充能！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:656
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:666
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "好吧。反正我也没想跟他们说话……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:668
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "飞船依旧只是飘浮在那里，在你等待超光速引擎充能的过程中，没有受到任何干扰。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:670
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:674
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:680
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "他们也太没礼貌了。进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:682
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你简直受不了这些怪异鱼人的厚颜无耻。他们明知道自己是那种看到附近随机出现的飞"
"船却不主动联络的家伙，晚上怎么还能睡得着觉？你下令进攻，外面那艘飞船察觉到你"
"的敌意，立刻准备自卫。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:686
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:694
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我希望不暴露行踪，谢谢。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:696
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“随你……便吧。”那个声音沉默了下去。你独自望着虚空，心里想着自己是多么想念那些"
"星辰。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:698
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:702
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_TURQUOISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:712
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"无尽的虚空始终笼罩着你，你在等待那个声音的指引。不过它并没有让你等太久：“谐合"
"者……就在这个信标处。只是……有点奇怪。这艘飞船本该是猎手，可他们……却没有表现出"
"任何敌意。需要我……驱散这片虚假的黑暗吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:715
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "动手吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:717
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"随着黑暗被驱散，那艘飞船却不断往黑暗深处退去；不过最终它放弃了，并向你发起通"
"讯：“我……不明白。猎物……就在这里，可黑暗之神的庇护却抛弃了我……”它看起来对此十"
"分激动。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:720
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你为什么不攻击我？你不是猎手吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:722
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"对方显得很惊讶：“你怎么会……”它顿了顿，“等等。这……这是一场考验。一场……信仰的考"
"验。黑暗之神希望我……证明我的虔诚。那么听着，让我的信仰……昭示天下！”谐合者切断"
"了通讯，他们的武器开始启动！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:725
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:731
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "看来你的黑暗之神已经把你抛弃了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:733
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它似乎思考了片刻。“说实话……我也一直在考虑抛弃它。消息传来……你们的‘叛乱’正源源"
"不断地攻入我们的领地……我们的教义本会让你认为这……是不可能的，然而……”启蒙者沉默"
"了一会儿。最终，它继续说道：“如果……如果黑暗之神已经辜负了我们，那么……留在这里"
"等死，又有什么意义？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:735
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:737
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它似乎思考了片刻。“说实话……我也一直在考虑抛弃它。消息传来……你们的‘叛乱’正源源"
"不断地攻入我们的领地……我们的教义本会让你认为这……是不可能的，然而……”谐合者沉默"
"了一会儿。最终，它继续说道：“如果……如果黑暗之神已经辜负了我们，那么……留在这里"
"等死，又有什么意义？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:745
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "这么说，你们其实不堪一击？进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:747
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "这黑暗……还有什么意义，假如……”它没有再说下去，但你也根本不在乎。你切断通讯，准"
"备发起进攻。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:751
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:759
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我不想去赌一个猎手的运气。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:761
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“说得……也是。”那个声音沉默了下去，你在等待超光速引擎充能时，心里有些紧张。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:763
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:767
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_DOUBTFUL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:776
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST_SHIP\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:779
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST_SHIP\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:784
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST_SHIP\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:787
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST_SHIP\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:794
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "“说得……也是。”那个声音沉默了下去，你在等待超光速引擎充能时，心里有些紧张。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:798
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/text"
msgstr "你还没来得及独处一秒，那个声音就立刻呼叫你，语气震惊：“陨石……在这里？还带着奇"
"怪的颜色……它们看起来完全迷失了方向。你……想看看吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:801
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "那就给我吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:803
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "黑暗渐渐消退，你得以亲眼看见这艘岩石飞船。它看上去略带水晶质感，通体漆成金色"
"，还带有一枚奇特的徽章……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:806
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "……我完全不知道这是什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:808
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这可不是你见过的任何一艘岩石族飞船。无论如何，他们向你发出了通讯，你看到的是"
"几个身着长袍的岩石族人。其中一个开口道：“你好，呃，联邦！没想到在这儿碰到你们"
"……你们不会碰巧知道，呃，这里是哪儿吧？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:810
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你们正处在一片由启蒙者占据的人造虚空之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:812
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他挠了挠头：“光……什么人？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:814
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "他们是一群崇拜一个被他们称为黑暗之神的深渊潜者教派。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:816
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"听到“教派”这个词，他拦住了你：“哦！你看，我就说吧！”他看向另一个岩石族人，“那"
"只自由螳螂说得没错，这里就是教徒虚空！”另一个岩石族人只是哼了一声。前者随即转"
"向你：“等等，如果这里是教徒虚空……你在这里干什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:818
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "呃……只是路过而已……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:820
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他眯起眼睛：“我敢肯定……你是来偷我们的神秘秘密的……哼，你别想得到！去搞你自己的"
"秘密，去占你自己的虚空去！”他们切断了通讯，武器开始上线，准备发起攻击！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:823
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:829
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_cultist\"]/text"
msgstr "（岩石异教徒船员）我跟好多教徒都是朋友。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:831
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_cultist\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他瞪大了眼睛：“兄弟！哦嗬，我现在肯定是在做梦！戈索克，扇我一巴掌！”第二个岩"
"石族人狠狠给了他一下，然后他就……直接昏死过去了。到底是昏了还是死了，你也说不"
"准。不管怎样，这位“戈索克”本来就话不多，转身离开了房间……可你还没反应过来，他"
"就已经登上你的飞船了！你的岩石族教徒解释说，他和戈索克是老相识了，而戈索克显"
"然早就受够了刚才那个岩石族人。那家伙真的死了吗……？无论如何，戈索克已经加入你"
"的船员！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:832
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_cultist\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "戈索克"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:836
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者教徒）我认识的教徒可多了去了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:838
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他盯着你的深渊潜者看了好一会儿，然后说：“这……该不会是套衣服吧？”他又看了看自"
"己的长袍。“说实话，我还挺想要一套的。我的衣柜里除了蓝色长袍就没别的了，来套鱼"
"人服倒也不错。”他眨了眨眼，“呃，我们刚才说到哪儿了？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:840
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "教派的事。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:842
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“啊，对！我超爱教派这些东西，这教徒虚空我怎么待都待不腻！”他看向屏幕外的舷窗"
"，你能看到他微微打了个寒颤。“话说回来，打个比方啊……要是有人真的待腻了这地方，"
"那该怎么，你懂的，离开这儿？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:844
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "“啊，对对对！我在那些……呃，‘神秘典籍’里看到过，给陌生人送点免费物资，有助于逃"
"出教徒虚空。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:846
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“那要是周围有陌生人的话，这办法就太有用了……”他挠了半天头，突然一脸恍然大悟，“"
"等等！你就是陌生人啊！”他转向另一个岩石族人，“那个……戈索克，把几件圣物送过去"
"，行吗？我们平时给陌生人的东西已经用完了。”然后他转回头对你说道：“多谢帮我们"
"离开这儿，刚才还以为我们彻底迷路了呢！”他们切断通讯，礼物已经发了过来……你最好"
"趁他们还没发现被骗之前赶紧溜，假设他们能反应过来的话。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:856
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/text"
msgstr "（水晶族船员）我和神是朋友。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:858
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一看到你的水晶族人，那两个岩石族人当场就晕过去了，重重砸在地板上。你一时不知"
"道该怎么办，然后其中一个醒了过来。可你刚松口气，他又第二次晕了过去。这样反复"
"好几次后，你觉得最好还是切断通讯……你的水晶族人面无表情地看着你，叹了口气，离"
"开了房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:862
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vortigon\"]/text"
msgstr "（沃蒂根）“你觉得我来这儿是干什么的？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:864
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vortigon\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“沃、沃蒂根大人？！您居然在这儿？说实话……您出现在教徒虚空里，简直再合理不过了"
"，大人！我向您致以最深的歉意，大人！”另一个岩石族人也歉意地哼了一声，他们随即"
"送过来一大堆杂七杂八的东西当作赔礼。沃蒂根翻了个白眼。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:873
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "“这里？就是你的坟墓，伙计。进攻！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:875
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那岩石族人眨了好几下眼，才反应过来。“哦——呵，原来是来真的是吧？戈索克！准备武"
"——”话没说完，他们就切断了通讯。看来是迫不及待要开战了……只不过，再急也急不过你"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:878
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:886
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "等等，我认得这艘船……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:888
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"等等，我认得这艘船……这是不熄余烬教派的船！他们发来通讯，画面里出现了几名岩石"
"族教徒。其中一个开口道：\"你好啊，呃，联邦佬！没想到在这儿碰见……你该不会知道"
"，咱们现在到底在哪儿吧？\""

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:890
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你们现在处在一片由启蒙者占据的人造虚空里。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:892
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他挠了挠头：“光什么？谁？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:894
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "他们是一群深渊潜者组成的教派，崇拜一个他们称之为黑暗之神的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:896
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他听到“教派”这个词就打断了你：“哦！你看，我就说吧！”他转头看向另一个岩石族人"
"，“那只自由螳螂说得没错，这里就是教徒虚空！”另一个岩石族人只是哼了一声。前者"
"又转回头看向你：“等等，如果这里是教徒虚空……那你来这儿干什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:898
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "呃……只是路过而已……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:900
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他眯起眼睛：我看你就是来偷我们的神秘机密的……你想都别想！自己去找秘密，自己去"
"找虚空去！他们切断通讯，武器开始充能，准备开战了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:903
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:909
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_cultist\"]/text"
msgstr "（教徒船员）我认识的教徒可多了去了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:911
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_cultist\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他眼睛一下子瞪大：兄弟！哦哦，我现在肯定是在做梦！戈索克，扇我一下！第二个岩"
"石族人狠狠一巴掌，他直接昏死过去，也可能是死了，你也说不清。不管怎样，戈索克"
"本来就话不多，转身离开了房间……可没过多久，他居然出现在你的船上！你的教徒船员"
"解释说，他和戈索克早就认识，而且他早就受够了刚才那个岩石族人。那家伙到底死没"
"死……无所谓了，戈索克已经加入你的船员！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:912
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_cultist\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "戈索克"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:916
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者教徒）我认识的教徒多了去了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:918
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他盯着你的深渊潜者看了好一会儿，然后说：“那该不会……是一套服装吧？”他又看了看"
"自己的长袍。“说实话，我还挺想要一件的。我的衣柜里除了蓝色长袍就没别的了，来套"
"鱼人装应该挺不错。”他眨了眨眼，“呃，我们刚才说到哪儿了？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:920
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "教派事务。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:922
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“啊，当然！我超爱教派相关的东西，这教徒虚空我怎么待都待不腻！”他看向屏幕外的"
"窗外，你能看到他微微抖了一下。“话说回来，打个比方啊……假设有人真的待腻了这教徒"
"虚空。那他们到底该怎么，你懂的，离开这里？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:924
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我呃，在神秘典籍里看到过，给陌生人送点免费的东西，有助于逃出教徒虚空。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:926
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“嗯，要是周围有陌生人的话，这办法倒挺有用……”他挠了半天头，脸上突然露出恍然大"
"悟的神情，“等等！你就是陌生人啊！”他转向另一个岩石族人，“喂，呃……戈索克，把那"
"些圣物送过去一些，行吗？我们平时送给陌生人的那些东西已经用完了。”然后他转回头"
"对你说：“谢谢你帮我们离开这儿，刚才还以为我们彻底困死在这了呢！”他们切断了通"
"讯，礼物也送了过来……你最好趁他们还没发现自己被骗之前赶紧离开。就当他们永远不"
"会发现吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:936
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/text"
msgstr "（水晶族船员）我和上帝是朋友。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:938
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"看到你的水晶族人，那两个岩石族人立刻昏了过去；砰的一声重重倒在地上。有那么一"
"瞬间你不知道该怎么办，然后其中一个醒了过来。接着你又不知道该怎么办了，因为他"
"们再一次昏了过去。这样循环了好一会儿，你觉得最好还是切断通讯……你的水晶族人面"
"无表情地看着你，叹了口气，离开了房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:942
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vortigon\"]/text"
msgstr "（沃蒂根）“你觉得我在这儿干什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:944
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vortigon\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“沃、沃蒂根？！您怎么会在这儿？说实话，您出现在教徒虚空里，简直再合理不过了，"
"大人！我向您致以最深的歉意，大人！”第二个岩石族人歉意地哼了一声，然后他们送过"
"来一堆乱七八糟的东西作为赔罪。沃蒂根翻了个白眼。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:953
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "这地方？就是你的坟墓，伙计。进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:955
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那岩石族人眨了好几下眼，才反应过来发生了什么。“哦——呵——呵，原来是这么回事，是"
"吧？戈索克！准备武——”话没说完，他们就切断了通讯。看来他们是迫不及待要开战了……"
"只不过，还是远没你这么迫不及待。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:958
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"loc_crystalhome\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:968
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:970
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“我也……不怎么喜欢看到岩石族人。”那个声音低沉了下去。你凝视着黑暗，心里盘算着"
"那艘岩石族人飞船不小心撞上你的概率有多大……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:972
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_EMBER_CULTIST\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

