"递了过来，当你靠近时，一股恐怖的气息萦绕在它周围。他们说……这是黑暗之主的礼物…"
"…这里面究竟藏着怎样的诡异力量？那个声音没有给出任何答案。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1392
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[6]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "那么……你们的灯光怎么样？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1394
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[6]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“这要求……还真是奇怪又具体。你刚刚……救了我们，还阻止了这块岩石的狂暴行径，所以"
"……我想我们可以相信你，把黑暗之主的……馈赠交给你。这是你应得的。”说完，他们花了"
"点时间拆下仅剩的几台还能运作的灯光，然后把它们递给了你。你一拿到手，至少可以"
"说，感觉……很不舒服。你唯一能确定的是，它们散发着某种诡异的能量，而那个声音对"
"此没有给出任何解释。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1401
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[6]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "他们根本就不明白，是吧？把他们炸掉。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1403
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[6]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“等等……求你——”通讯骤然中断，他们的飞船先是扭曲变形，随即断成两截。死寂震耳欲"
"聋，你尽力搜刮物资，却所剩无几……真是浪费时间。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1415
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你抵达时，只见橙色的闪光一次次刺破黑暗，每次间隔数秒。这样过了一会儿，那个声"
"音艰难地对你开口：“同族……在这里……正被……被屠杀……一艘岩石飞船……型号我从未见过，"
"在猎杀他们。它……似乎对武器火焰免疫。我……我知道你的生存才是首要任务，联邦成员…"
"…可是……我的族人……”它没能把话说完。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1418
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "照亮前路，剩下的交给我。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1420
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它的声音里带着哽咽，却又透出一丝希望：“谢……谢谢你，真的谢谢你。”随着一阵强烈"
"的紧迫感，虚空迅速退去；一条布满残骸的道路出现在你面前，启蒙者的飞船四处损毁"
"，你意识到，自己正直面一名岩石圣骑士。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1423
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"它的声音哽咽，却又透出一丝希望：“谢……谢谢你，真的谢谢你。”强烈的紧迫感袭来，"
"虚空迅速退去，一条布满残骸的道路出现在你眼前，启蒙者的飞船四处损毁，你意识到"
"，自己正面迎上了一名岩石圣骑士。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1425
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你继续向前推进，圣骑士飞船发出通讯：“联邦舰队。我不知道你是如何迫使这股邪恶的"
"黑暗退去的，但这已无关紧要。长老们要求净化这片虚空中的所有无信者，而你，就在"
"其中。安心吧，我们的惩戒将会迅速降临。”他们切断通讯，准备发起攻击……你会成为他"
"们神圣征途上的又一块垫脚石，还是终结这场疯狂的人？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1427
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1433
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "转念一想……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1435
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你还没来得及行动，圣骑士飞船便再次发来通讯：“联邦之人。我不知道你是如何让这股"
"污秽的黑暗消退的，但这无关紧要。长老下令，必须净化这片虚空里的所有无信者，而"
"你，就在其中。安心吧，我们的惩戒会来得很快。”他们随即切断通讯，准备发起攻击……"
"你会成为他们神圣征途上的又一个牺牲品，还是终结这场疯狂的人？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1437
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1445
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我做不到，对不起。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1447
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“可是，他们……”它顿了顿，“我……”没有再说下去。气氛有些尴尬，但……“武器无法击穿”"
"这句话，实在没法让你对胜算有信心。话说回来，所有岩石族飞船不都多少能免疫武器"
"攻击吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1450
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1454
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_PALADIN_CRUSADE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1462
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/text"
msgstr "虚空瞬间被抽离，一艘启蒙者飞船出现在视野中，那个声音说道：“猎手……来了。做好准"
"备。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1466
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1468
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "但让你意外的是，他们向你发出通讯：“等等！等等，等等，等等！”你从没见过深渊潜"
"者说话这么快……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1470
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "等等。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1472
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们松了口气，继续说道：“天啊，哇……你真的来了！等等，你不认识我，呃……我是你的"
"超级粉丝。我在深渊潜者星域的一场战斗里见过你，不是……不是这一场……”他们看向屏幕"
"外，咽了口唾沫，“……呃，另一场。我真的不喜欢这场。不管怎样！从那以后我就一直跟"
"着你。你看，我还偷了一艘这些花哨的邪教徒飞船！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1475
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那艘“花哨的邪教徒飞船”差点害你送命……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1477
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“是啊，但……这很酷，不是吗？我现在简直在cosplay你的死敌啊！”他们眨了几下眼睛，"
"然后说道，“现在想想……这主意好像不怎么聪明，对吧？也许我就不是干这种跟踪勾当的"
"料……”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1479
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "如果你想更擅长跟踪我，我有一些诀窍。我可是个专业跟踪者。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1481
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他们眼睛一亮，“真的吗？！哇！我本来觉得你已经够酷了……没想到我们居然这么有共同"
"语言！”他们满怀期待地看着你。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1483
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/text"
msgstr "（隐形）首先，你得搞到一个这玩意儿。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1485
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/text"
msgstr "“哦，我真正用来跟踪的飞船上就有一个！我不太清楚这艘抢来的船有什么装备，反正就"
"是顺手劫了……总之，我可比你这个专业跟踪者领先一步呢！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1487
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/text"
msgstr "（先进隐形）你的跟踪能力跟我比起来，简直不值一提。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1489
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们吓得往后一跳，“整整十五秒，最少？！哇，你真的是专业的！”他们顿了顿，记下"
"了什么，“好！等我离开这里，一定要好好练习隐形。说到……离开这里……这地方真的让我"
"毛骨悚然。我下个星域再见吧。不过你肯定看不到我，我马上就要变成专业跟踪者了！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1491
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1493
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不过在我走之前，这艘船上可是有各种好东西！我反正也用不上，而且我怎么能放过帮"
"助联邦的机会呢？我现在也算你故事里的一员了！让我翻一翻，看看能找到什么……他们"
"翻找了一会儿，随即给你发送了一堆乱七八糟的物资……其中还包括一件武器！“好了，专"
"业跟踪大佬！祝你好运，我们回头见！”说完，他们便离开了这个星系。那个声音对你说"
"道：“至少可以说……是个很有魅力的小家伙。”你几乎能感觉到，它的话语背后藏着一丝"
"极淡的笑意……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1503
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "看来，终究没什么我能教你的了……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1505
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哦……别难过呀，在我心里你依然是最专业的跟踪大佬！”他们环顾了一下四周，接着说"
"道，“不过我想，这就意味着我得自己琢磨跟踪这门手艺了。但我不会放弃的！下个星域"
"再见，到时候我的跟踪能力一定会强到你根本发现不了我！祝你好运，暂时先拜拜啦！”"
"他们离开了信标区域，只留下你独自一人……除了那个声音，它对你说道：“至少可以说……"
"是个很有魅力的小家伙。”你几乎能感觉到，它的话语背后藏着一丝极淡的笑意……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1513
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "其实……更像是个正在受训的跟踪者。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1515
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哦……别难过呀，在我心里你依然是专业跟踪大神！”他们环顾了一下四周，然后继续说"
"道，“不过我想，这就意味着我得自己琢磨跟踪这门本事了。但我不会放弃的！我们下个"
"星域见，到时候我的跟踪能力会强到你根本发现不了我！祝你好运，暂时再见啦！”他们"
"离开了信标区域，只剩下你独自一人……除了那个声音，它对你说道：“至少可以说……是个"
"很有魅力的小家伙。”你几乎能感觉到，它的话语背后藏着一丝极淡的笑意……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1523
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "你有没有想过别再跟踪别人了？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1525
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "他们短暂地愣了一下，看着你：“那我不跟踪你的话，怎么知道接下来会发生什么事啊？"
"”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1527
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你可以跟我来。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1529
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他们一脸震惊地回答：“然后去打打杀杀？抱歉，我真的很佩服你，可是……我觉得我不是"
"拯救世界那块料。跟踪安全多了！不过还是很谢谢你邀请我……”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1531
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1533
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“好！我下定决心了。我要离开这里，好好练习我的跟踪术……在此期间，你一定要保重，"
"好吗？我们下个星域见！不过你应该……呃，不会看到我的。”说完，他们便离开了这个星"
"系，那个声音对你说道：“至少可以说……是个很有魅力的小家伙。”你几乎能感觉到，它"
"的话语背后藏着一丝极淡的笑意……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1541
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "你可以过你自己的生活！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1543
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "他们坏笑一下：“你的生活可比我有意思多了！你收拾掉这么多坏蛋，感觉整个宇宙都在"
"围着你转呢……不过我还是很谢谢你这番心意。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1545
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1547
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“好！我已经下定决心了。我要离开这里，好好练习我的跟踪术……在此期间，你一定要保"
"重，好吗？我们下个星域见！只不过你应该……呃，不会看到我的。”说完，他们便离开了"
"这个星系，那个声音对你说道：“至少可以说……是个很有魅力的小家伙。”你几乎能感觉"
"到，它的话语背后藏着一丝极淡的笑意……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:1561
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_ENLIGHTENED_SUPERFAN\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
