#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2158
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_LEVIATHAN\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "这巨兽果真淌出财富。虽只是微薄些许，在你皇家的荣光面前黯然失色……可即便如此，"
"也仍是财富。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2161
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_LEVIATHAN\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "盛宴吧，我灵魂中的深渊……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2166
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_LEVIATHAN\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "这巨兽果真淌出无尽财富。虽只是微薄点滴，在你皇家的荣光面前黯然失色……可即便如"
"此，也仍是真金白银。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2169
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_LEVIATHAN\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "吞噬吧，我灵魂深处的深渊……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2176
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_LEVIATHAN_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"几小时后，你醒了过来。你记得的最后一件事是……拆解飞船？那个声音对你喊道：“我们"
"得……离开这儿，马上，你这个蠢货！叛军……要追上我们了！”每句话都带着轻蔑，你醉眼"
"朦胧地环顾四周……几艘叛军飞船的残骸已经飘浮在外面的太空中。你在这里待了多久？"
"就在这时，一支小型的MFK精英舰队正朝着信标驶来；你心想，是时候赶紧离开这里了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2184
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_LEVIATHAN_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "快跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2190
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你强迫自己继续拆解飞船，试图填满你那吞噬一切的贪婪……可这远远不够。永远都不够"
"。没有任何东西能满足你。你是被虚空吞噬了……还是你自己，已然变成了虚空？那个声"
"音开口道：“我们……最好还是赶紧离开吧，真的。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2194
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "屈服吧，化身贪婪，成为它的具象。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2196
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“叛……叛军正在逼近。难……难道这不值得担心吗？”那个声音向你恳求着。它在哀求，可"
"你充耳不闻；它的话语，不过是这片黄金之海中几滴微不足道的银水罢了……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2200
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "沉浸在这一切奢华璀璨的光辉之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2202
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "听！一只污秽的巨怪，闯入了你的财宝之中！这头野兽必须被斩杀，以免它玷污这片圣"
"地……冲啊，兄弟们；尽情屠戮，畅饮这可憎之物的鎏金之血！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2205
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2213
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD_GREED_THREE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "忏悔吧；化身意志力，成为它的化身。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2219
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"无处不在的虚空向你致意。看来你很受欢迎，因为那个声音也随之响起：“一片……残骸区"
"域似乎包围了这座信标。这里有宝贵的资源……前提是你愿意付出时间，而时间才是最珍"
"贵的……资源。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2222
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "残骸……资源……废料！让我来！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2224
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你和你的船员开始行动，成功拆解了不少飞船。再继续下去，就有被叛军追上的风险……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2227
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "继续干。还有战利品要抢！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2231
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我没事，可不想太贪心了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2233
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“真是……明智的决定。”那语气听着几乎像是赞许……无论如何，你带着刚到手的战利品准"
"备离开这座信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2239
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不想打扰逝者，我就不去了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2241
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你能想象出那个声音在你脑海里挑了挑眉，对你说道：“真的吗？我……还以为你早就没有"
"这种理智了。算我……小看你了。”这是赞美？还是讽刺？不管怎样，你都不明白他们为什"
"么非要这么讨人厌。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2244
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_WRECKYARD\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
