#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2640
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_FUELDUEL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "不如我直接把你炸飞怎么样？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2642
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_FUELDUEL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“等等，什么？这有什么好……”你直接切断通讯，朝这艘燃料运输舰开火。即便在太空真"
"空里，燃料还是从舰体内部抽出氧气，瞬间燃起大火……整艘船被猛烈的爆炸彻底摧毁、"
"吞噬。恐怕连一点残骸都剩不下……真是可惜。死寂的太空也认同这一点。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2651
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_FUELDUEL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "怪瘆人的。算了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2653
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_FUELDUEL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "拒绝喊话之后，一切归于寂静。你试图安慰自己，你偏爱这种彻底的、无处可逃的、震"
"耳欲聋的沉默，想让自己好受一点。但不知为何，这并没有用。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2655
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_FUELDUEL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
