#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2678
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2681
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2688
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "等你完成打捞回收后，那个声音对你说道：“谐离-17……这个名字寓意很多，却又……什么"
"都没说。”它没有再详细解释，只留下你独自琢磨这些含义。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2690
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DISPARITY\"]/text"
msgstr "（谐离船员）他们之前一定是来这里寻找谐离成员的。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2692
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DISPARITY\"]/event/text"
msgstr "没错。虽然他们误入歧途，但这里确实是黑暗之神的领地。这算不上是宇宙中最糟糕的"
"搜寻地点……可你还是会好奇，他们来到这里究竟想要达成什么目的。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2696
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "你不确定……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2698
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION_SHIP_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "唉，看来这个谜团只能留到以后再解开了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2704
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/text"
msgstr "这一次，那个声音向你提出了一个问题：“这些奇怪的……金属人。你……对他们了解多少？"
"”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2707
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "看情况。你说的是哪种金属人？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2709
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你的族人……称他们为半械族。而我的族人……可以说相当封闭。我们只通过新来的同族或"
"是贡品，才听闻外界和他们的行事方式。尤其是这些……半械族……我们对他们十分陌生。"
"但不管怎样，我相信他们其中一艘……飞船就在这个信标处。”就连这个神秘的声音，也遇"
"上谜团了？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2711
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "听起来挺有意思的，让我看看他们。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2713
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"黑暗退去，你眼前出现了一艘半械族飞船——而且还不是普通型号，是一艘精英舰。他们"
"向你发出通讯：“身份：联邦。当前区域遭遇联邦的概率：趋近于零……表明存在外部动机"
"。请求说明联邦动机。”他们想知道你为什么会在这里……他们到底在怀疑什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2716
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "说来话长。简单来说，我被深渊潜者的黑暗之神选为贡品了。现在只想设法逃出这片星"
"域。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2718
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "它短暂处理了一下信息：“联邦目标：逃离。半械族目标：与联邦目标对立。提议妥协："
"半械族协助联邦，联邦协助半械族。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2720
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你想要我做什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2722
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“要求：不得向任何人透露你遭遇了半械族。”这听起来更像是命令，而非请求……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2724
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "当然。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2726
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "它的躯体微微一动：“要求：达成。半械族指令：信任联邦并提供协助。所需协助：未知"
"。更新要求：告知所需协助。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2728
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_ENGI_INVESTIGATION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "请求维修。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:2730
