#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3383
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN_SHOP_BOUGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"那只蛞蝓人看起来毫不在意：“哇哦，你……呃，把我所有货～～都买光了。再这样～～买"
"下四十七单，我这周的指标就完成啦。看～～来我得等下一批货～～了。”你有种预感，"
"那批货短时间内肯定到不了……不过话说回来，他那些能神奇变形的武器和模块，是真的"
"挺酷。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3387
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标处时，你惊讶地发现有人正在向你发送通讯请求。有人透过黑暗注视着你……而"
"那个声音并未给出任何回应。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3390
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "接受这道神秘的通讯呼叫。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3392
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你接受了通讯，结果却被广告狂轰滥炸？“接下来0.3秒～～内，所有赫克塔工业（"
"Hektar Industries™）产品统统优惠1.2%！”还有“你绝对不会相信你所在区域的超值优"
"惠！它们可能只持续几～～秒！不保证。”之类的广告一条接一条。为什么蛞蝓人连写字"
"都要把S音拖得这么长？广告浪潮平息后，你终于能和一个真正的人对话了……如果你把赫"
"克塔的员工也算作人的话。“哟～～。联邦军的人跑这儿来干嘛？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3394
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你在这儿干什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3396
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“呃？你没收到公司的备忘录吗？业务扩张～～之类的，找最近的星云开个店。这片星云"
"还挺漂亮的，只不过顾客～～嘛……就跟不存在～～一样？你要是愿意买～～点东西的话"
"，就是第一个客人了。你真该～～买点。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3398
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你应该意识到这根本不是星云，对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3400
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你能想象得出，如果它可以的话，此刻应该正眨了眨眼——就那样站在那里，一言不发……"
"随后它开口道：“那、那你是什么意思？这、这又是～～什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3402
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这是一片无尽的黑暗虚空，由一位残酷无情的神明维系，只为让我们永远承受折磨。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3404
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "它花了好一会儿才消化这句话，最后答道：“所、所以～～……这、这算、算是～～在赫克"
"塔工业的管、管辖范围之外～～吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3406
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯，也许吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3408
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“如果不是的话，我就得在这儿干活了。否～～则的话，我就随便摸鱼之类的；但我可不"
"想冒任何风～～险。除～～非你是来让比利本人接电话赦免我的，不然我还是希望你要"
"么买～～点东西要么赶紧走。最好是，呃，买～～点东西。照这～～样下去，我好像要"
"完不～～成指标了……”唉，又一只蛞蝓人沦为了打工奴隶。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3410
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好吧，我想我还是买点东西吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3414
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/text"
msgstr "（心灵控制）呜——我是比利，我在此赦免你——！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3416
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你还是得想象一下它正盯着你眨眼睛的样子，“你知道的，这～～招对我没用，对吧？你"
"到底打不打～～算买东西？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3418
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好吧，行吧……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3422
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我没事，抱歉。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3424
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“那我们……呃，到底为什么在聊天啊？”你自己也不太明白，于是结束了通讯。这虚空里"
"不是到处都是嗜血的猎手吗？这只蛞蝓族怎么就待在这儿浪费氧气？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3426
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3430
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3436
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/text"
msgstr "（比利）“呜——我是比利，我在此赦免你——！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3438
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"蛞蝓族从椅子上往后一翻，摔在了地上。还没等爬起来，它就趴在地上大喊：“比～～利"
"先生，先～～生！您确～～定吗，先～～生？”比利看上去有点不好意思，草草点了点头"
"。蛞蝓人爬起来，跳起了一段怪异的蛞蝓舞：“哇呜！我自～～由啦！喂，联邦佬，把我"
"的货～～都拿走吧，我反正再也用不上了！我真～～的自由啦！来，我、我把它们都弹"
"～～射到太空里给你，我想～～想应该可以！”你在通讯器里听到一阵声响，可……这片虚"
"空依旧遮蔽着你的视线。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3440
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嘿，声音？能帮个忙吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3442
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_HEKTAR_SALESMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"过了一会儿，它回应道：“抱歉……我刚才也从椅子上摔下去了。只不～～过……是笑摔的。"
"总之，没问题，我会……强行使这片虚假的黑暗退去。”黑暗果真消散了，你能看见一把赫"
"克塔武器和几个组件漂浮在太空中……可就是不见飞船。你也注意到通讯已经中断了。看"
"来那家伙已经跑了。"

