msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_DARKGOD\"]/text"
msgstr "这里有种说不上来的怪异……就算不去管外面那片翻涌、能吞噬一切的暗影之海，也依然"
"如此。这只是你的直觉。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3551
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_DARKGOD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "可能没什么事……对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3553
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_DARKGOD\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你飞船货舱里传出的刺耳声响，听着绝不像是没事。你起身前去查看，船员们也跟了上"
"来。在那里等着你的，是一堆废料？你还没来得及琢磨它是哪来的，那个声音就开口了"
"：“污秽，配得上污秽之神的诱惑。拒绝这份怜悯。它在玩弄你。”可这毕竟是免费的废"
"料啊……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3555
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_DARKGOD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "接受这份礼物。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3557
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_DARKGOD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "谁在乎这是不是神明的怜悯？废料就是废料！那个声音没有再多说，但说实话，谁在乎"
"呢？你在这儿尽情享用这些废料时，它尽管闹脾气好了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3565
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_ENLIGHTENED_DARKGOD\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
