#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3622
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT_ENLIGHTENED_WIN\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr "击败启蒙者之后，你转身发现异种猎人已经消失不见。你无法确定他们是逃离了信标，"
"还是仅仅退回了虚空之中，最终只留下你独自一人，置身于这片寂静里。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3626
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT_ENLIGHTENED_WIN\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"击败启蒙者之后，其中一名异种猎人向你发来通讯：“哟哟哟，这是也要去捕鱼吗，联邦"
"佬？算我一个，我看好你。”他转过身去，“伙计们，我这就出——”通讯突然中断，但看来"
"你多了一名新船员！四周的寂静也仿佛充满了敬畏。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3634
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT_SLUG_WIN\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"你已经战胜了异种猎人，但看起来启蒙者在战斗中逃走了……不过你仍然做了正确的事，"
"保护了弱者。或者说，呃，更弱的家伙？那些家伙还在外面四处猎杀路人……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3638
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT_SLUG_WIN\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"你战胜了异种猎人，其中一位启蒙者向你发来通讯：“外来者……不惜以身犯险来拯救我们"
"？这必定是……黑暗之神降下的征兆，赞美祂的名。若……是祂的旨意，那就顺其自然吧。”"
"你一时没明白他们在说什么，紧接着他们就瞬移到了你身后！多了一名新船员，还差点"
"吓出心脏病……真是买一送一的特别待遇。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3646
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"抵达求救信标处时，那个声音向你呼唤：“同族……需要援助；猎手已成了……猎物。一艘蛞"
"蝓飞船正在攻击他们，滥用他们……看穿这片虚假黑暗的能力。你……要出手相助吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3649
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "分开虚空，我来处理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3651
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"虚空被拨开，两艘飞船随即映入眼帘。启蒙者虽遭受重创，却仍在坚持……你注意到这些"
"并非普通的蛞蝓人，而是异种猎人，他们必定是来这片领地猎杀深渊潜者的。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3653
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "攻击异种猎人。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3655
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你冲到两艘飞船之间，将武器瞄准异种猎人，明确表明了你的意图。准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3658
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3664
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "攻击启蒙者。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3666
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "他们毫无防备！你冲到两艘飞船之间，将武器瞄准启蒙者，而异种猎人似乎并不介意你"
"抢走他们的目标。启蒙者准备自卫！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3669
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3677
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "抱歉，我承受不起这场战斗。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3679
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“我……也很抱歉。如果我能……做点什么来救下他们就好了……”被你一心想要拯救的人追杀"
"，这滋味一定不好受……等等。这不就是在说你吗，不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3682
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3686
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SLUG_ASSAULT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3695
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_TRAP\"]/text"
msgstr "没过多久，那个声音便惊慌地说道：“有个异种猎人……就在这里，这求救信号是个陷阱！"
"”虚空迅速退去，你刚好及时躲开了袭来的炮火……准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3699
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_TRAP\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3706
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_STATION\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3709
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_STATION\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3714
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_STATION\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3717
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_STATION\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3724
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_STATION_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你刚完成打捞，那个声音便对你说道：“我……很高兴看到那个恶棍被终结。为了……满足它"
"那冷漠自私的心智，竟然拿我的同族做实验。愿它所受的诅咒……也如它当年那般残酷无"
"情。”阿门。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3742
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/text"
msgstr "你的深渊潜者进入了空间站，而你在外面等候。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3744
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "等等。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3746
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "最后，甲壳族回来了……独自一人。“测……试……很抱歉地告诉你，你的……深渊潜者……”它语"
"塞哽咽，艰难地开口。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3748
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "这种事时有发生，我明白。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3750
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "它抬起头，“嘿嘿嘿，我只是逗你玩呢。他们没事。等着，我这就去把他们带过来。”你"
"这是搞什么啊……？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3752
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，再来一次。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3754
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这一次，你不用等太久。甲壳族带着你的深渊潜者一同回来了，还递给你一些废料：“拿"
"着，算是辛苦你的酬劳。我知道你们联邦佬就爱这些破烂。”哦，是吗？是你的博士学位"
"让你看出来的？话虽如此……这废料还真不少……想生气也难了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3761
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "你这个混蛋，我要杀了你！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3763
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "它连忙后退大喊：“哇，哇，别激动！我只是在逗你呢！他们没事！我这就去把他们带过"
"来！”你这算什么……？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3765
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，再来一次。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3767
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这一次你没等多久。甲壳族带着你的深渊潜者回来了，还递给你一些废料：“拿着，算是"
"辛苦你的酬劳。我知道你们联邦佬就爱这些破烂。”哦，是吗？是博士学位让你看出来的"
"？不过……这废料还真不少……想生气也难了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3778
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/text"
msgstr "你的深渊潜者进入空间站，你在外面等候。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3780
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "等等。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3782
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"最后，甲壳族回来了……独自一人。“我就直说了……彻底搞砸了。他们死了。不过我有能力"
"补偿你；科学向来都是有备无患的。”它转身去拿补偿，这时那个声音愤怒地对你喊道："
"“这个……这个凶手……侵入了我们的领地。把我的同族诱进了它的谎言巢穴。用白银铺就他"
"们的坟墓。我……没什么请求，外人……但它必须下地狱。你来当法官、陪审团……还有刽子"
"手。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3784
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3786
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "甲壳族拿着补偿转向你，“我真心希望我们能翻过这一页。如果能让你好受些……他们是为"
"科学而死的。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3788
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "收下补偿然后离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3790
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "甲壳族几乎没有表现出任何同情，但你还是收下了补偿，离开了空间站。你拖着那袋废"
"料，发出刺耳的叮当碰撞声，可随之而来的沉默，却比这噪音更加沉重。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3797
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "你回到飞船上，却看见你的深渊潜者因为克隆舱的缘故完好无损……看来你狠狠坑了那个"
"甲壳族一把！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3802
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "那么……那到底是什么科学？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3804
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"甲壳族扯了扯它的领带：“呃，其实吧，我来到深渊潜者的领地，是为了研究一种奇特的"
"……嗯，你可以称之为‘气体’的东西，它完全笼罩了这片区域。”它的目光飞快地扫过房间"
"四周。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3806
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么……你有什么发现，医生？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3808
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这可怜的家伙瞬间慌了神。“那、那个……‘气体’，根本无法解释。它……是物质形态的，这"
"一点可以肯定；它能被摧毁，也能被操控。可真正难住我们的，是它的……智能。不管是"
"真实存在，还是我们拟人化的想象，它似乎遵循着某种逻辑，或者说，某种思考方式。"
"除此之外，我们也搞不清它的起源，还有它的目的……”它还在喋喋不休。它真以为你在认"
"真听吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3810
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "干掉它。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3812
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "枪声在整个空间站里回荡，甲壳族话没说完就应声倒地，一命呜呼。死有余辜。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3814
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "收下这份“补偿”，然后离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3816
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"天啊，这也太解气了……你拿着废料，在心里打算好了要为牺牲的深渊潜者准备一篇悼词"
"，然后返回了飞船。等一切平静下来，那个声音简短地对你说：“我……也很满意。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3823
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "你回到飞船上，却看到你的深渊潜者因为克隆舱完好无损……看来你狠狠坑了那个甲壳族"
"一把！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3828
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "把这个地方和这笔沾满鲜血的钱，全都烧为平地。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3830
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"点燃整个空间站根本不费吹灰之力……这里到处都是化学品的刺鼻气味。烈火熊熊燃烧时"
"，你将一切尽数吸入肺中……化身成了复仇本身。愤怒，有了形体，可……你放慢动作，深"
"深吸了一口气。一切都结束了，你赢了。你可以把这个受诅咒的地方和它邪恶的过往统"
"统抛在身后；你用正义的怒火与烈焰，完成了对它的最终审判。当复仇的火焰舔舐着你"
"的脸颊时，烈火的中心凝聚出一团物质。你看着它不断塑形，最终变成了一个熟悉的轮"
"廓……那是……你的深渊潜者？这是幻觉吗？烟雾造成的假象？还是错觉？像是在回应你的"
"疑惑，那团身影从火焰中升起，径直从你身边走过；它毫发无伤。你敬畏地凝视着，动"
"弹不得，而此刻正吞噬着你的火焰，正用它贪婪的怀抱欢迎着你……而你……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3832
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3834
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你醒了过来。你正坐在空间站里，四周一片寂静。你是什么时候睡着的？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3836
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "回去继续等候。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3838
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH_SCIENCE_DREAM\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你没等多久。甲壳族就带着你的深渊潜者回来了，还递给你一些废料：“喏，算是给你的"
"补偿。我知道你们联邦佬就喜欢这些破烂。”哦，是吗？是你的博士学位让你得出这个结"
"论的？不过话说回来……这废料还真不少……想生气也难了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3860
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你抵达了求救信标处，那个不耐烦的声音对你说道：“这里……根本没有紧急情况。是那些"
"……搞科研的家伙，你们叫他们甲壳族，想引人注意。你……要理会他们吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3863
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "当然，我可喜欢甲壳族了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3865
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"随着虚空退去，你本以为会看到一艘飞船，可这里竟然建了一整座甲壳族空间站！他们"
"发来通讯：“联邦的人？居然在这里……真是费解。不过我发出求救信标时，倒也没指望会"
"是你们。对了，你们船上该不会正好有深渊潜者吧？或者是一些他们那种……比较奇特的"
"武器？随便哪样都行。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3868
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你为什么这么问……？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3870
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你能感觉到它在努力翻了个白眼。“我当然是为了科学才需要它们，不然还能为什么？你"
"到底有没有？没有的话，你就是在浪费我的时间。”这家伙还真是没耐心……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3872
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DEEPONES\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者）当然，没问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3876
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/text"
msgstr "（黑暗武器）当然，没问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3878
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它看到这东西显得欣喜若狂：“这技术诡异至极，起源更是离奇——要是深渊潜者的话可信"
"的话，他们说这是他们那位‘黑暗之神’的馈赠。就算真是如此，我也一点不意外。这些"
"武器似乎操控着一种与这片区域的气体相似、甚至完全相同的物质；而且……这种气体好"
"像拥有自己的意识……”它顿了顿，或许是意识到自己说得太多，清了清嗓子才继续道：“"
"给我一点时间研究一下，很快就好。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3880
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等着甲壳族完成研究。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3882
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"显然它确实说到做到，没花多久就回来了：“我的假设看来是对的；这些武器里的气体与"
"构成这片区域的气体的确是同一种物质。我把结果和之前拿到的另一把武器做的试验比"
"对过了。既然我已经拿到需要的信息，这东西现在还给你吧；我觉得它对你这样的人来"
"说……会更有用。就当是给你的补偿。”甲壳族把你的武器还给了你，而且还多给了一把！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3885
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "谢了，科学！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3887
msgid ""
