#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3889
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "它们让我感觉充满力量。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3891
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“力量……会腐蚀人心。伪神深知这一点，所以它在最能体现价值的地方，赐予力量……记住"
"这点。”那声音随之沉寂，只剩下你、手中的武器……还有那份力量，再度相伴。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3896
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我好像就是总能找到它们。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3898
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“这……绝非巧合，伪神想要的是你……你，以及你的忠诚。这些馈赠……本就是为了腐化你；"
"你要保证……不要被它们侵蚀。”那声音随之沉寂，只剩下你、手中的武器……还有那份谜团"
