#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3903
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "它们很有趣！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3905
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“能从……消灭敌人的过程中找到乐趣。对一名士兵来说……这是个好品质，可对一个人而言"
"……却很可怕。不过，至少……你很诚实。”那声音随之沉寂，只剩下你、手中的武器……还有"
"那份乐趣，再度相伴。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3916
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/text"
msgstr "（灵魂瘟疫武器）这能用吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3918
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你把被灵魂瘟疫感染的武器递给甲壳族，他们困惑地看着它：“不，这东西怎么可能有用"
"？这只是一把普通武器，被……灵魂瘟疫……物质……病毒……污染了而已……呃啊——”他们一碰到"
"它，身体就开始……变异，泛起虹彩般的光泽，随后只是瘫在原地低声呻吟。你不想把他"
"们独自留在这里、无法自救，于是把他们带上了飞船，但是……他们绝对出了问题。那个"
"声音虽然沉默，你却能感觉到，对方很可能也被这件事惊扰了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3919
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "我没事"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3923
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "我就不用了，谢谢。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3925
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "甲壳族一言不发地结束了通讯。那个声音也陷入了沉寂。然而在这片寂静之下，你仿佛"
"听见……深渊深处，有什么东西正在响动。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3927
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3931
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
