#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3939
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr "“我在乎吗？我可不是来陪你应付这些毫无意义的问题的。你要是想来为科学做点贡献，"
"那就动手。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3941
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[5]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DEEPONES\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者）行，没问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3945
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[5]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/text"
msgstr "（黑暗武器）行，没问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3947
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[5]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它看到这件东西时显得十分兴奋：“诡异的科技，起源更加离奇，如果深渊潜者的话可信"
"的话。他们声称这些是他们那位‘黑暗之神’的馈赠，就算这是真的，我也不会感到意外"
"。它们似乎在利用一种与该区域气体相似——就算不完全相同——的物质；而且，这种气体"
"似乎拥有自己的意识……”它顿了顿，或许意识到自己说得太多了，清了清嗓子继续道：“"
"给我一点时间研究一下，我会尽快。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3949
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[5]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等待甲壳族完成。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:3951
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_SHELL_RESEARCH\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[5]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"显然，它确实说得很简短，因为没过多久它就回来了：“我的假设似乎是正确的；这些武"
"器内部的气体与构成这片区域的气体确实是同一种。我已经将我的发现与之前的试验结"
"果进行了比对，之前的试验涉及我设法得到的另一把武器。既然我已经从中获取了所需"
"的信息，现在它可以归还给你了；我想它对你这样的人来说可能会更……有用。就当是给"
"你的补偿吧。”甲壳族把你的武器还给了你，而且还多给了你一把！"

