"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT_RETRIBUTION\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/text"
msgstr "没有任何回应响起。但不知为何，你亲眼看着你的船体在你眼前修复了部分伤痕……你刚"
"才究竟经历了什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4088
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT_RETRIBUTION\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-15\"]/text"
msgstr "我们……我们做到了吗？我们赢了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4090
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT_RETRIBUTION\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-15\"]/event/text"
msgstr "没有回应响起，只剩下你独自一人，置身于这片寂静之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4094
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT_RETRIBUTION\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-99\"]/text"
msgstr "我们……我们做到了吗？我们赢了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4096
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT_RETRIBUTION\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-99\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"寂静震耳欲聋，甚至带着不祥的预兆。片刻之后，最后一击狠狠砸在你的船体上！损伤"
"看似微乎其微，可……那些阴影竟会做出如此怯懦的行径，这让你心头一紧。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4104
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/text"
msgstr "你已经抵达求救信标处，可是……那道声音却沉默了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4107
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "这是虚惊一场吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4109
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "啊，你突然明白了——陷入险境的人，正是你自己。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4114
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "淹没……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4116
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "问题是……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4119
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "在……之中"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4121
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……谁会来救你？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4124
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "……这……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4126
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一阵刺耳的声响将你吞没……是金属摩擦？还是金属被撕裂的声音？你无法确定。你正努"
"力稳住心神，一个遥远的声音向你呼喊：“外来者！外来者，听我说……伪神正在撕扯你的"
"船体！那片黑暗，你千万不能……”它还想说下去，可你再也听不清了……这头痛欲裂。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4130
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我的……船体？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4132
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你意识到自己身在何处，也明白发生了什么。有什么东西正在击穿船体；你不清楚那是"
"什么，但那个声音暗示，那就是黑暗本身。如果真是这样……你还有什么希望能逃离这片"
"虚空？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4134
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/text"
msgstr "（先进武器）轰碎这该死的黑暗，绝不留情！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4138
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"engines\"]/text"
msgstr "（先进引擎）想要逃离这看似绝境的深渊……就必须一试！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4142
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"shields\"]/text"
msgstr "（先进护盾）挺直腰杆——我们是坚固壁垒，早已准备好抵御这场风暴。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4146
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"PALADIN_ARMOR_PLAYER\"]/text"
msgstr "（圣骑士护甲）哈，我倒要看看它敢不敢试试！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4150
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DARKGOD_WEAPONS\"]/text"
msgstr "（黑暗武器）我不畏惧黑暗，因为驾驭黑暗的正是我！服从我！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4154
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DEEPONE_LIGHTS\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者之光）黎明破晓，黄昏降临——成为令阴影畏惧的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4158
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DREAD_LIGHTS\"]/text"
msgstr "（恐惧之光）黎明既至，黄昏降临——成为令阴影胆寒的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4162
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dddeepone_chosen\"]/text"
msgstr "（天选船员）“请允许我们……通行，黑暗之神。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4166
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者信徒）“黑暗之神，与我们同在……”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4170
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\"]/text"
msgstr "（烙疤者）“反抗伪神……没有什么能比这更让我快意。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4174
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\"]/text"
msgstr "（女杰）“他们想碾碎我们的希望？那我们就碾碎他们的！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4178
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_HAPPYHOLIDAYS\"]/text"
msgstr "（哈皮·霍利戴丝）“哦，我们来把它拆解掉！”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4182
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ENLIGHTENED_JUDGMENT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[13]/text"
msgstr "祈求奇迹降临……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4200
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING_FIGHT\"]/gotaway/text"
msgstr "这对奇怪的双人组跃迁离开。看来下次你得再快一点才行。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4204
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4207
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4212
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4215
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4222
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "击败这对奇怪的组合后，你在他们的残骸中搜寻着有用的东西……可惜一无所获。只剩下"
"一片寂静。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4228
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你沉默等待着那个声音开口，过了片刻。你正以为这里一定空无一物时，它终于说话了"
"：“这……实在古怪。我的一位同族……与人类共用一具躯体。你……要去见他们吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4231
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "好，那就去看看他们到底在搞什么名堂。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4233
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"虚空分开，映入你眼帘的竟是一艘民用飞船。对方发来通讯，你发现另一端确实是一名"
"人类与启蒙者信徒。那名体格健壮、肌肉发达的人类开口道：“嗬嗬！联邦的人，还是个"
"变元者！你也是来探寻此地真相的吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4236
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "差不多是这样。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4238
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他双臂交叉，爽朗地大笑起来：“好吧，朋友，你来晚了！我和我的爱人刚刚发现了这里"
"最大的秘密……”他朝那位启蒙者信徒示意，对方羞涩地动了动，轻笑出声：“嗯……没错。"
"这是我们同族之间严守的秘密……那就是禁忌之恋！谁能想到……外来者竟会如此浪漫……”他"
"们相拥在一起，让你不禁感到有些尴尬。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4240
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "保持沉默。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4242
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"男人松开拥抱，转向你：“不管怎么说，幸会！我叫科尔——是这该死的多元宇宙里最伟大"
"的探险家！”你敢说从没听说过他……科尔继续说道：“我身边的是莉莉丝……我的准新娘，"
"也是我有幸遇见的最美丽的姑娘。”你从未见过深渊潜者脸红，但莉莉丝此刻确实做到了"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4244
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "幸会！我自己也算是个探险家……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4246
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"科尔夸张地挑了挑眉：“哦？真的吗？”他摸了摸自己浓密的胡须，“好吧，同为狂热探险"
"家，我有理由相信此地藏着一个秘密。这片虚空之后，存在着另一个位面，更加深邃……"
"更加黑暗。我的爱人也听说过它。”他再次示意莉莉丝，莉莉丝抬起头说道：“我……偶然"
"听到长老们提起过。那个国度……我们的贡品被送往那里，而馈赠……也会从那里送来。那"
"片领域……正是黑暗之神所在之地。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4248
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "真有意思。你们打算去找它吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4250
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哈！要是不去找，我还敢称自己是最伟大的探险家吗！”科尔摆出一副豪迈的姿态，再"
"次放声大笑，但随即他的神色一变，微微凑近通讯屏幕，“我不知道另一边会有什么在等"
"着我们，说实话，也不确定我们还能不能回来。如果你打算来找我们……”他顿了顿，输入"
"了些什么，你的飞船传来一声轻响，收到了一组详细的超光速信号特征，“……你就知道该"
"怎么找到我们——前提是我们还活着。”科尔坐直身体，神色又轻松起来，“我可不会正经"
"建议你跟着我们去这么凶险的地方！只不过，如果你真的听从了真正探险家的召唤，碰"
"巧踏入了黑暗之神所在的领域。再说了，我们甚至都不能完全确定那地方真的存在！”科"
"尔再次笑了起来，可莉莉丝却显得有些不安。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4253
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我会记住的。祝你好运，科尔。也祝你好运，莉莉丝！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4255
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"莉莉丝因为你向她致意而露出了喜色：“谢谢你……呃，联邦的人，对吗，亲爱的？”科尔"
"用力点头：“没错！整个多元宇宙里仅存的少数高尚派系之一。把我们的位置托付给他们"
"，是最值得信赖的，亲爱的。”这番话似乎让莉莉丝安心了一些。两人向你道别，随后跃"
"迁离开了信标区域，只留下你独自面对这片黑暗。而这片黑暗之中，不止有你，还有那"
"个声音再次响起：“真是……美好。我……祝他们一切顺利。”你也同样如此希望。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4268
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "才不是，我只是来捡破烂的。攻击这对情侣！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4270
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "男人皱起眉头：“哈！我还以为联邦是个值得尊敬的组织。别担心，亲爱的，我会带我们"
"离开这里！”你察觉到他们的引擎轰然启动，他们想逃跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4273
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4281
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "莉莉丝看着你。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4283
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "她显然不想看到这里的任何东西……为了安抚她，你告诉那个声音你没兴趣。它叹了口气"
"，“随……你吧……”然后便沉默了。你独自留在这片黑暗之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4285
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_ENLIGHTENED_HORRORS\""
