"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "那个原本显得很感兴趣的声音叹了口气：“随……你吧。”它陷入了沉默，只留下你独自置"
"身于这片黑暗之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4299
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_KYRANDLILITH_MEETING\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
