#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4312
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "精英联邦飞船轰然解体，你只能暗自祈祷，船上遗留的那些恐怖存在已经与它一同覆灭…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4315
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4320
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "精英联邦飞船空空如也——既没有恐怖怪物，也没有任何生命——你只能暗自祈祷，这真的"
"是它们的终点……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4323
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4330
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"然而，你还没来得及细想刚才目睹的一切，联邦飞船的残骸中就有什么东西吸引了你的"
"目光。不，这不仅仅是吸引注意——那东西散发的璀璨光芒，竟让你感到心神完全被攫住"
"了。这股难以抗拒的吸引力牵引着你的视线，让你渐渐看清了它的模样……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4332
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "它……太美了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4334
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "那枚美妙的水晶碎片，原本就在军官的外套里……此刻它就在废墟之中。呼唤着你，召唤"
"着你上前，投入它的怀抱。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4336
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是的，我……我从来不需要别的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4338
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你凝视着水晶碎片空灵的核心，完全沉醉在它无与伦比的光辉之中，周遭的一切仿佛都"
"渐渐消散……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4340
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4342
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4346
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4348
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "空气中弥漫着灰烬与硫磺的气味。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4350
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哈！不一直都这样吗？你是不是总爱在盔甲里藏玫瑰之类的东西？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4352
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "才没有。只是……事情本来不必变成这样，你明白吗？这绝对不是我原本设想的样子。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4354
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，事情就是这么发展的，不是吗？咒骂过去毫无意义。坦白说，咒骂前世也一样没"
"用。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4356
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4360
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "谁说我们无计可施了？那大家伙还能怎么样，杀了我们？这混账东西早就清楚它做不到"
"。你迟早会想出办法的，伊芙。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4362
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它显然杀不死我们，可是……弗，比这更可怕的地狱多的是。我是说，你看看六号——她也"
"许喜欢战斗，可要是永远这样下去呢？就因为她曾心生不满，还敢有所行动？就算她的"
"意志永远不会垮，那她的盔甲呢？她的身体呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4364
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"她很坚强的，伊芙，你清楚的，不是吗？我们又不是在这里干等着，无所事事，等她哪"
"天撑不住倒下。我们一定会离开这里，也会把六号从她那麻烦里救出来。反正都是一回"
"事，对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4366
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "对。都是一样的。我会……我会想出办法的，然后……我们会……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4368
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

