"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哦……真的吗？你是说那个被他们打上叛徒烙印的家伙？嗯……我可没在这里任何地方看见"
"过它。你……觉得它是觉得无聊了吗？或许……丢下你自生自灭了？”一阵停顿，原本就轰鸣"
"的笑声变得几乎震耳欲聋，随后那声音继续说道：“那……不是很有趣吗？哦……我就知道我"
"会喜欢你。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4616
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "听着——我现在要处理的事情够多了。有话直说，不然我就开飞船跃迁离开这里。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4627
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/text"
msgstr ""

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4631
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，可是……你为什么在乎我怎么死？你不是应该为了你的那位神明，来杀了我吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4633
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4637
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "默默祈祷这个怪家伙真的会被彻底击倒。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4639
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4643
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "犹豫着同意了。你还有时间。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4645
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"周围的笑声掀起一阵骚动，那个声音也变得兴奋起来：“哦……太棒了。有趣、特别……还这"
"么出色！黑暗之神果然……很会选人，不是吗？既然这样……那就把航向稍微往左调一点，"
"就……朝着那个方向飞一会儿。别担心……会撞到什么东西。我会……密切盯着的！可不想让"
"你……撞到什么，然后死得很惨。那确实会很有趣，只不过……这么多年我也算明白了一件"
"事，那就是……并非一切都要有趣。通常是这样，但……并非永远如此。”那个声音连同此刻"
"令人发狂的笑声一同消失了——再次只留给你一片诡异的寂静。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4647
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么……开始吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4649
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你竭尽全力按照那个声音模糊的指示行事，径直朝一个方向飞去。一开始相当平静——直"
"到某一刻，它突然在你脑海里尖叫，让你猛地向左转向。你立刻照做，回荡的笑声在你"
"周围重新轰鸣起来，持续了令人难受的几秒钟。你……实在不太享受这段航程。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4652
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4654
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不过到最后……你周围的黑暗像是自行分开了，你迎面遇上的不是别人，正是一艘联邦精"
"英战舰。他们在这里做什么？不，更重要的是——你又在这里做什么……？你到底被寄予了"
"什么样的期待？直到此刻，你才真正想起要问这个问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4657
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "嘿，呃……声音老兄？能解释一下吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4659
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它对你的发问显得很惊讶，仿佛本以为你会盲目行事。“哦……好吧，当然。我之前提到过"
"其他迷失的灵魂，对吧？这一个看起来也很特别。只不过……没那么有趣。他觉得从我这"
"里偷走些贵重东西是明智之举。我……想要拿回来。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4661
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "如果你能这么轻易地毁掉我，那为什么不直接毁掉他们？他们在这儿不也一样“没有眼睛"
"”吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4663
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4667
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "深吸一口气，回应联邦战舰的通讯呼叫。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4675
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "好吧，随便了。我自己会想办法的。呼叫联邦战舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4685
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "拒绝。你已经受够了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4687
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你周围响起一片嘘声，那个声音毫不掩饰地表达着失望：“哦……看来你终究还是没什么意"
"思。也许我……才是这里真正的小丑。算了，随便吧。你就……跟那个叛徒之类的家伙好好"
"相处吧。”四周陷入寂静，你这辈子从未如此庆幸过这一刻。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4689
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "终于，能清静一会儿了……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4691
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的放松时光被一阵呼喊声打断，自从进入这片星域就一直陪伴着你的那个声音——不再"
"那么刺耳——插了进来：“外来者！外来者！你……还好吗？发生什么事了？我……我有好一阵"
"子都看不到你了。我一直都在……往最坏的地方想。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4693
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "说实话，就是个混蛋而已。特别烦人的家伙——还自带一整套精神笑声背景音，乱七八糟"
"的全都有。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4695
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_SURPRISE_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“精神层面的……？那……听起来像是启蒙者中的长老。他们本身就很强大……但并非我原本预"
"想的那种威胁。我还以为……是伪神找上了你，然后……”\n"
"\n"
"那个声音又说了好一会儿，你花了不少时间安抚它，向它保证你真的没事，也没有什么"
"所谓的邪恶机械之神吸走你的灵魂。一切最终归于平静，而当这一切结束时，你已经迫"
"不及待要将超光速引擎开到最大功率了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4711
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"屏幕上出现了一名联邦军官，正如你所预料的那样，但他的模样立刻让你吃了一惊。他"
"不只是看起来憔悴不堪——而是看起来已经好几天没合过眼了。不过，就算他注意到了你"
"在盯着他看，也没有表现出来。“知道吗，在这种地方看到一张友善的脸，真是让人松了"
"口气。是你做的吗？那些……呃……那些阴影？我从没见过它们就这样消失。说真的，我……"
"我从没见过它们有过任何动静。这里就只有……黑暗，一片又一片的黑暗，然后……更多的…"
"…”军官望向外面的虚空，你能感觉到，他肯定已经在这里待了很久。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4713
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "大概算是吧。我能……问问你在这里做什么吗？你看起来就差一步就要撑不住了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4715
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他的眼神慌乱地与你对视。“我？我……不行，抱歉。我不能告诉你。我……我答应过她不会"
"说的。如果你也来到这里，肯定能理解，对吗？你……你一定明白的，不是吗？”\n"
"\n"
"你疑惑地看着他，他疲惫的神情瞬间变得绝望。“告诉我，我……我没有疯，对不对？你也"
"能听见那些声音，是吗？你也能看见那些幻象，对不对？那些声音！那些……幻象！它们"
"不肯放过我！它们停不下来……”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4719
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嘿！没事的，真的。我在这里也听到过声音——事实上，其中一个声音就是把我带到这儿"
"来的！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4721
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你这么说，本想能给他一点安慰，可他的眼睛反而因恐惧而睁大。“它们……？是她……？不"
"，我遵守了我的承诺！我做到了，我发誓！我拿到了面具，就按照那该死的纸条吩咐我"
"的那样，然后……不，不，不——求你了，我发誓！我会去拿更多！我只是需要更多时间！"
"我只是……需要……”\n"
"\n"
"这名军官停下了疯狂的呓语，注意力重新回到你身上，脸上露出冰冷的神情。“我只是需"
"要献祭更多。比我……天啊，对不起，大家。我……”他缓缓伸手，想去摸外套口袋里的什么"
"东西……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4725
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，你在干什么？你知道我现在是站在你这边的，对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4727
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这句话似乎暂时触动了他。“我的……朋友？不，我……我没有朋友。再也没有了。自从……我"
"……”这名军官痛苦地皱起眉，终于掏出了他一直想去拿的东西——一块像是玻璃或水晶的碎"
"片。不管那是什么，它看上去……很美。他将它越握越紧，一股难以言喻的能量从他身上"
"向外扩散，通讯信号突然中断——就在这时，他的战舰武器开始启动！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4730
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDENLIGHTENED_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_TALKTOFED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "看来我们只能用最麻烦的方式解决了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4746
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4752
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//textList[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "虚空瞬间被撕裂，一艘启蒙者战舰出现在视野中，那个声音响起：“猎人……接近中。做好"
"准备。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4753
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//textList[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "你看着黑暗退去，那个声音向你呼喊：“外来者！启蒙者……正在接近！”你发现了那艘飞"
"船，并做好了战斗准备。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4754
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//textList[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "虽然那个声音没有说话，却依然迫使阴影退去；一艘启蒙者战舰从虚空中浮现，武器已"
"然待命。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4755
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//textList[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED_TEXT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr "一瞬间，万籁俱寂……紧接着，那个声音大喊：“外来者，伏击！”你险之又险地避开了袭"
"来的炮火，黑暗渐渐退去……他们来了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4756
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//textList[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED_TEXT\"]/text[5]"
msgstr "这个信标处感觉……有点不对劲。果然，没过多久，虚空被推开……你和一艘启蒙者战舰正"
"面相遇！真是一语成谶。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4757
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//textList[@name=\"HOSTILE_ENLIGHTENED_TEXT\"]/text[6]"
msgstr "抵达信标后，你收到附近一艘启蒙者战舰的通讯呼叫：“死吧……外来者！向黑暗之神献祭"
"！向长老们献祭！”还真是“含蓄”……虚空退去，你准备迎战。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4762
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "最后一击落下，这艘无畏舰轰然坠毁；你看着它的舰体崩解，被它曾誓言守护的黑暗彻"
"底吞噬。你，胜利了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4765
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4770
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "船员尽数阵亡，这艘无畏舰撑不了多久；你看着无数时空裂隙在它的舰体上撕裂开来，"
"将其吞噬在它曾誓言守护的黑暗之中。你，胜利了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4775
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4783
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "最后一击落下，这艘无畏舰轰然崩塌；你看着它的舰体碎裂，被它曾誓言守护的黑暗彻"
"底吞噬。你，胜利了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4786
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4791
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "船员全部阵亡，这艘无畏舰撑不了多久；你看着无数时空裂隙在它的舰体上撕裂开来，"
"被它曾誓言守护的黑暗所吞噬。你，胜利了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4796
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4805
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "它坠落，坠落，一再坠落……而你，依然屹立于此——活着！你果然非同凡响……？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4808
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//ship[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4816
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO_CREWKILL\"]/text"
msgstr "你以为自己终于赢得了胜利，可就在这时，那名残存的英雄体内突然爆发出一股能量——"
"不知为何，它竟然重新站了起来……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4819
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO_CREWKILL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4821
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO_CREWKILL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……还有它那群满怀希望的随行人员中的一部分。这股在你血管里奔涌的感觉……这，才是"
"拼死一战的滋味！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4829
msgid "data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"DDTRUEHERO_LASTSTAND\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"就在那名英雄踉跄之际，它稳住了身形：“别……别想这么快结束！我拒绝……去死，拒绝……"
"让整个宇宙毁灭！”你看着深渊潜者从黑暗中现身，敌方战舰的伤势也在不断愈合……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4835
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "在残骸中，你又发现了一件黑暗武器……只不过，这一件你从未见过。不知为何，它看上"
"去完好无损……不管怎样，它现在属于你了。你只希望它没有被诅咒……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4842
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4844
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"烙疤者看向你，发出胜利的呐喊：“如此……伪神的爪牙便败亡了！他们虽与我同族……却早"
"已屈从于那股邪恶的力量。我会……为他们曾经的模样哀悼，而非……他们如今的样子。”它"
"环视四周，接着说道：“只是……战斗尚未结束。只要伪神一日不倒，这场战争就永远不会"
"落幕。不过，既然这片虚空将归于虚无，他们彻底挣脱伪神的掌控……想必会对其力量造"
"成沉重的打击。”话音落下，它陷入了沉思。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4848
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "现在怎么办？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4850
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它又思索了片刻，然后开口：“或许……我最好不要回到我的族人那里，至少……现在还不行"
"……”它看向你，“……但这并不代表我不能与同族并肩。我……会与你站在一起，投入你的战"
"斗……就像你曾为我而战一样。更何况，拯救这个现实世界……也意味着拯救我的族人。带"
"路吧……同族！”身边多了一位新的盟友，你准备离开这片黑暗虚空。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4852
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4854
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你正要离开，整个现实却仿佛骤然停滞。这让你想起初次进入这片星域时，烙疤者将你"
"定住的场景……只不过这一次，响起的是另一个声音，它只说了一个词……“够了。”你感觉"
"到周遭的一切都在加速，外部的空间本身也在扭曲……那片虚空，竟莫名变得更加明亮。"
"你意识到自己正以光速被拖拽着穿过它！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4856
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓紧了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4869
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4871
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "遗憾的是，烙疤者在战斗中牺牲了……你别无选择，只能继续前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4873
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4875
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你正要离开，整个现实却骤然停滞。这让你想起初次进入这片星域时，烙疤者将你定住"
"的场景……只不过这一次，响起的是另一个声音，它只说了一个词：“够了。”你感觉到周"
"遭的一切都在加速，外界的空间本身也在扭曲……那片虚空，竟莫名变得更加明亮。你意"
"识到自己正以光速被拖拽着穿过它！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4877
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_GOOD_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓紧身边的东西！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4890
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "在残骸之中，你又发现了一件黑暗武器……只是这一件你从未见过。不知为何，它看上去"
"完好无损……无论如何，它现在属于你了。你只希望它没有被诅咒……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4897
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4899
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你正要离开，整个现实却仿佛骤然停滞。这让你想起当初刚进入这片星域时，那个声音"
"将你定住的场景……只不过这一次，响起的是另一个声音，它只说了一个词：“够了。”你"
"感觉到周遭的一切都在加速，外界的空间本身也在扭曲……那片虚空，竟莫名变得更加明"
"亮。你意识到自己正以光速被拖拽着穿过它！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4901
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_NEUTRAL_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓紧点！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4912
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你周遭的时间仿佛停滞了，然后……一个全新的声音向你呼唤，你感觉似曾相识，却又想"
"不起在哪里听过：“你……让我很感兴趣。来吧，我欢迎你投入我的怀抱。”你感到周围的"
"一切都在加速，外界的空间本身也在扭曲……那片虚空，竟莫名变得更加明亮。你意识到"
"，自己正以光速被拖拽着穿过它！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4920
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT_DREADNOUGHT_TRUEHERO_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "抓紧了！"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4929
msgid "data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/text"
msgstr "你终于抵达了出口……"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4932
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/text"
msgstr "问问那个声音，现在会发生什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4934
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/text"
msgstr "它慌忙回答：“这里……有点不对劲。我……”它的语气听起来像是慌了。“……我想……他们是来"
"找我的。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4936
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "他们？是谁？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4938
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我们的族人里流传着……被伪神选中之人的传说。要……彻底献身于它，献身于它所代表的"
"一切……执行它的意志。以它的名义……毁灭它的敌人。我想……他们现在是来找我了。你……"
"必须走，如果你想逃掉的话。我感谢你……为我、为我的族人所做的一切。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4940
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你会怎么样？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4942
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它的语气蒙上了一层阴郁，“我……无所谓。从来都……无所谓。只要我的族人平安……只要我"
"的族人真正自由，我的命运……无关紧要。我只愿他们能抓住这次……机会，永远不要再回"
"归那位黑暗之神。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4944
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "不，不能就这样。现在不行。我会和你并肩作战，为你，也为启蒙者而战。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4946
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它看上去有些惊讶……却又并非全然意外。在一同穿越这片星域的途中，它早已目睹你为"
"启蒙者所做的一切，它明白……它信任你。“很好，外来者……不，你早已不再是外来者。若"
"我们注定死在这里……那便以同族之名，战死于此。”随即，一名身负无数伤痕的深渊潜者"
"出现在你面前……你终于与一直对话的那个声音，面对面相遇了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4948
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那我……该怎么称呼你？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4950
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它用手遮住带伤的眼睛，闷哼一声回答道：“你……以前问过。如果你真的需要一个名字来"
"称呼我……我的族人在传说里叫我烙疤者……那些都是可怕的故事，用来吓唬小辈做噩梦的"
"。那些故事背后的真相……本身也同样可怕。”它望向外面的虚空，放下手，“他们……来了"
"。”"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4951
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "战痕累累"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4953
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4955
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你看着伤痕者抬手一挥，外界的阴影被尽数驱散；取而代之的是，另一股阴影盘踞而来…"
"…一艘巨大的、深渊潜者风格的战舰正在逼近。虽然设计风格很熟悉，但整艘船没有任何"
"光亮，也毫无色彩，这让人心神不宁。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4959
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "做好准备。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4961
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"无畏舰传来通讯：“外来者。献祭。你庇护……叛徒。你意欲反抗。我们的主……注定胜利。"
"”通讯中断，他们的武器开始充能……全是黑暗造物。伤痕者与你对视，说道：“我们最好…"
"…别让他们的邪恶武器击溃我们。做好准备，同族……战斗吧！为了启蒙者！”说完，它离"
"开房间，准备迎战。无畏舰不断逼近，你知道，你也该行动了……在黑暗最肆虐之处，成"
"为一盏明灯。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4965
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"4\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4983
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/text"
msgstr "问问那个声音，现在会发生什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4985
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它没有回应，你看着外界的黑暗被驱散……一艘飞船从中浮现，正是你刚进入这片星域时"
"见到的那一艘。那个声音随后说道：“现在……我们分道扬镳吧。这片虚假的虚空已经被叛"
"军占据，我的族人……将被迫逃离。他们需要……一位引路人，带他们走向光明。我必须……"
"现在就去找他们，但愿他们……愿意倾听。永别了，外来者……谢谢你。”这个声音最后一次"
"归于沉寂，飞船也重新退回黑暗之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4987
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "准备离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4989
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你转身离开房间，准备驶离这片星域时……你感觉到了什么。一种不祥的预感，末日将"
"至的气息……一道新的阴影从黑暗中浮现。一艘巨大的深渊潜者制式战舰正在逼近。虽然"
"设计风格很熟悉，但没有任何光亮，也毫无色彩，这让人感到不安。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4992
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这是什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4994
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"无畏舰发来通讯：“外来者。献祭。你与……叛徒勾结。你图谋……摧毁我主。但你可以安心"
"，我主……会赐你一场仁慈的死亡。”他们切断通讯，武器开始上线……你发现其中一种武器"
"的设计从未见过，但已无暇细想。无畏舰准备发起攻击，而你，也在迎接终局的到来。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:4999
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-3\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5009
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/text"
msgstr "问问那个声音，现在会发生什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5011
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它没有回应，你看着外界的黑暗被驱散……一艘飞船从中浮现，正是你刚进入这片星域时"
"见到的那一艘。那个声音随后说道：“现在……我们分道扬镳吧。即将到来的战斗里，我的"
"族人会需要我……倘若这片虚假虚空之外的世界，有你一半冷酷无情的话。不过，我还有…"
"…最后一个请求，外来者……”它停顿了漫长而令人不安的片刻，“……别再回来了。”说完，"
"这个声音最后一次归于沉寂，飞船也重新退回黑暗之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5013
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "准备离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5015
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你转身离开房间，准备驶离这片星域时……你感觉到了什么。一种不祥的预感，末日将"
"至的气息……一道新的阴影从黑暗中浮现。一艘巨大的深渊潜者制式战舰正在逼近。虽然"
"设计风格很熟悉，但没有任何光亮，也毫无色彩，这让人感到不安。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5018
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这是什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5020
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"无畏舰发来通讯：“外来者。献祭。你与……叛徒勾结。你图谋……摧毁我主。但你可以安心"
"，我主……会赐你一场仁慈的死亡。”他们切断通讯，武器开始上线……你发现其中一种武器"
"的设计从未见过，但已无暇细想。无畏舰准备发起攻击，而你，也在迎接终局的到来。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5025
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-12\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5035
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-99\"]/text"
msgstr "总算到时候了。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5037
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-99\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你早已准备好离开这该死的虚空。可偏偏，这片寂静却另有安排。你看着外面的黑暗被"
"推开……一艘飞船从中显现，正是你刚进入这片星域时见过的那一艘。这家伙到底想干什"
"么？"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5039
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-99\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我受够了它的纠缠。把它炸掉。"

#: src-en/data/events_enlightened.xml:5041
msgid ""
"data/events_enlightened.xml$//event[@name=\"ENLIGHTENED_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"the_scarred_judgment\""
" and @lvl=\"-99\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一发炮弹径直击穿了那艘飞船，但在本该断裂成两半、轰然解体的地方……它却没有溃散"
"。那个声音再次对你说话，而它的飞船正违抗着死亡：“原来……原来是这样吗？仅仅……一"
"发炮弹而已……”它话语间带着可怜的咳嗽，“告诉我，外来者……或者，不管你究竟是什么…"
"…你离开……这片星域之后，打算做什么？”外面的飞船开始剧烈震颤。"

